
April is the month that comes before what?,May,9,7
April is the fourth month of the year, and comes between March and May.
1. April begins on the same day of week as July in all years and also January in leap years.
2. April's flowers are the Sweet Pea and Daisy.
3. At the end of the month, Central and Northern European cultures celebrate Walpurgis Night on April 30, marking the transition from winter into summer.

 April in poetry 
Poets use April to mean the end of winter.
